### **CEO Vision & Strategic Alignment**

Analysis of Mighty Networks' leadership commentary reveals a core philosophy: **building agile, flat, high-aptitude organizations powered by AI.** This aligns perfectly with HR.com’s domain.

*   **"Hiring for attitude over experience" (Keily Blair):** This is the #1 talent debate within our community. We provide the audience living this problem daily.
*   **"Eliminating the squidgy layer of middle management":** Our deep engagement data on organizational design and flattening hierarchies fuels this very conversation.
*   **"Building for her" & AI/ML Focus:** Inclusion and AI are the two most urgent topics for HR leaders. We own the data on what works and what fails.

**The Synergy:** Mighty Networks provides the agile, AI-powered platform. HR.com provides the mission-critical professional domain, engaged audience, and proven economic model. Together, they create the definitive platform for the future of professional work.

